		Dos brasileños y un argentino: así se sorteó el destino de Barcelona SC, Liga de Quito e Independiente del Valle en las copas Libertadores y Sudamericana	</h1>
	

	<div class="entry-subhead">
					<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="author-avatar"><img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/531954e42648e53f2212905e44a8fc63?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/531954e42648e53f2212905e44a8fc63?s=192&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-96 photo' height='96' width='96' loading='lazy'/></span><span class="byline"><span>por</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://wordpress-462131-1753247.cloudwaysapps.com/author/quenoticias/">Quenoticias</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2021-06-01T00:00:00-05:00">1 de junio de 2021</time></span>			</div><!-- .meta-info -->
