				<div class="main-content">

					
			<figure class="post-thumbnail">

				<img width="950" height="475" src="https://wordpress-462131-1753247.cloudwaysapps.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Copas-Libertadores-y-Sudamericana.jpeg" class="attachment-newspack-featured-image size-newspack-featured-image wp-post-image" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://wordpress-462131-1753247.cloudwaysapps.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Copas-Libertadores-y-Sudamericana.jpeg 950w, https://wordpress-462131-1753247.cloudwaysapps.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Copas-Libertadores-y-Sudamericana-300x150.jpeg 300w, https://wordpress-462131-1753247.cloudwaysapps.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Copas-Libertadores-y-Sudamericana-768x384.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 950px) 100vw, 950px" />						<figcaption>Copas Libertadores y Sudamericana. Cortesía.</figcaption>
					
